high_descs: Turn left, go forward to the wall, turn right, go forward, turn right to the island where the fork is.
Take the knife above the fork from the island counter.
Move a step to the left and face the island.
Cut the closest lettuce on the island counter into slices.
Turn left, go forward to the counter, turn right, go forward, turn left at the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn left, go forward, turn left, go forward, turn left to island counter where the lettuce is.
Take a slice of lettuce from the island counter.
Turn left, go forward to the counter, turn right, go forward all the way, turn right, go forward, turn left at the fridge.
Chill the lettuce in the fridge. Take the lettuce from the fridge.
Turn left, go forward to the counter, turn right, go forward, turn right at the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink in the lower left corner.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of lettuce in a sink.

high_descs: Turn left and cross the room until you reach the wall, then turn right to walk between the counter and kitchen island, ending facing the island.
Pick up the sharp knife from the center of the island by the lettuce.
Take a step to the left while carrying the knife.
Use the knife to slice the head of lettuce.
Turn left and move to stand in front of the kitchen sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn around and move back around the island to stand in front of the lettuce you just sliced.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the island.
Carry the slice of lettuce around the island to the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the lettuce on the second shelf, close the door, and then open the door and remove the lettuce once chilled.
Carry the lettuce to the kitchen sink.
Place the lettuce in the sink to the left of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Move a cold piece of lettuce to the sink by a knife.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the far side of the kitchen island, then face it.
Pick up the knife from the island.
Take a step to the left and face the lettuce.
Cut the lettuce on the island with the knife.
Bring the knife with you and move to the kitchen sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Go back to the island and face the lettuce where you sliced it.
Pick up a piece of lettuce from the island.
Bring the lettuce with you over to the black fridge.
Open the fridge and put the lettuce on the second shelf from the bottom, close the door and let it get cool, then take the lettuce out of the fridge again.
Bring the lettuce over to the kitchen sink.
Put the lettuce in the kitchen sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a piece of cold lettuce in the sink.
